stnNat.description: This MIB module describes managed objects of Spring Tide Networks Network Address Translation.

stnNatL2Table.name: stnNatL2Table
stnNatL2Table.description: A list of NAT L2 entries.

stnNatL2Entry.name: stnNatL2Entry
stnNatL2Entry.description: Entry contains information about a particular NAT L2.

stnNatL2IfIndex.name: stnNatL2IfIndex
stnNatL2IfIndex.description: This ifIndex is that of the VcLink/L2 that was NAT Enabled.

stnNatL2InsidePktMisses.name: stnNatL2InsidePktMisses
stnNatL2InsidePktMisses.description: The number of packets received from the 'inside' whose translation was unknown and needed to be learned

stnNatL2InsidePktHits.name: stnNatL2InsidePktHits
stnNatL2InsidePktHits.description: The number of packets received from the 'inside' whose translation was known.

stnNatL2OutsidePktMisses.name: stnNatL2OutsidePktMisses
stnNatL2OutsidePktMisses.description: The number of packets received from the 'outside' whose translation was unknown.

stnNatL2OutsidePktHits.name: stnNatL2OutsidePktHits
stnNatL2OutsidePktHits.description: The number of packets received from the 'outside' whose translation was known.

stnNatL2UntransInsidePkts.name: stnNatL2UntransInsidePkts
stnNatL2UntransInsidePkts.description: The number of packets received from the 'inside' that could not be translated because their source addresses were not among the valid inside addresses.

stnNatL2UntransOutsidePkts.name: stnNatL2UntransOutsidePkts
stnNatL2UntransOutsidePkts.description: The number of packets received from the 'outside' that could not be translated because the was no existing translation availible.

stnNatL2InsideAlgPkts.name: stnNatL2InsideAlgPkts
stnNatL2InsideAlgPkts.description: The number of packets received from the 'inside' that required Application Level Gateway (ALG) processing specific to protocol or application.

stnNatL2OutsideAlgPkts.name: stnNatL2OutsideAlgPkts
stnNatL2OutsideAlgPkts.description: The number of packets received from the 'outside' that required Application Level Gateway (ALG) processing specific to protocol or application.

stnNatL2FlowId.name: stnNatL2FlowId
stnNatL2FlowId.description: This is the internal flow identifier associated with this VcLink/L2 Interface.(STN use only)

stnNatGroupTable.name: stnNatGroupTable
stnNatGroupTable.description: A list of group based NAT entries.

stnNatGroupEntry.name: stnNatGroupEntry
stnNatGroupEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular group based NAT.

stnNatGroupSubnetIfInstance.name: stnNatGroupSubnetIfInstance
stnNatGroupSubnetIfInstance.description: A sequence number that identifies a sub-network interface entry in the table.

stnNatGroupOutsideBaseAddress.name: stnNatGroupOutsideBaseAddress
stnNatGroupOutsideBaseAddress.description: This is the first outside IP address in the range of outside addresses that packets from the inside have their source address translated to.

stnNatGroupOutsideEndAddress.name: stnNatGroupOutsideEndAddress
stnNatGroupOutsideEndAddress.description: This is the last outside IP address in the range of outside addresses that packets from the inside have their source address translated to.

stnNatGroupInsideBaseAddress.name: stnNatGroupInsideBaseAddress
stnNatGroupInsideBaseAddress.description: This is the first inside IP address in the range of inside addresses that packets from the outside have their destination address.

stnNatGroupInsideEndAddress.name: stnNatGroupInsideEndAddress
stnNatGroupInsideEndAddress.description: This is the last inside IP address in the range of inside addresses that packets from the outside have their destination address translated to.

stnNatGroupTransMode.name: stnNatGroupTransMode
stnNatGroupTransMode.description: Indicates if translations for this NAT group are handled with a static address to address mapping, a pooled address mapping, or a port based mapping (PAT). The translation is relinquished due to inactivity for the pooled and port based cases.

stnNatGroupAddrIdleTime.name: stnNatGroupAddrIdleTime
stnNatGroupAddrIdleTime.description: The number of seconds that a translation can be idle This value is ignored for static NAT.

stnNatGroupAddrTransAvailable.name: stnNatGroupAddrTransAvailable
stnNatGroupAddrTransAvailable.description: The number of outside Addresses available in the pool for translation. This value is ignored for static NAT.

stnNatGroupMaxFtpSessions.name: stnNatGroupMaxFtpSessions
stnNatGroupMaxFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that can be translated from the 'inside' at one time. This value is only for client sessions initiated from the inside.

stnNatGroupMaxFtpSessionsPerInsideAddr.name: stnNatGroupMaxFtpSessionsPerInsideAddr
stnNatGroupMaxFtpSessionsPerInsideAddr.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that can be translated from one 'inside' address at one time. This value is only for client sessions initiated from the inside. (0 means field is ignored.)

stnNatGroupFtpControlSessionIdleTime.name: stnNatGroupFtpControlSessionIdleTime
stnNatGroupFtpControlSessionIdleTime.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that can be translated from the 'inside' at one time. This value is only for client sessions initiated from the inside.

stnNatGroupCurrentFtpSessions.name: stnNatGroupCurrentFtpSessions
stnNatGroupCurrentFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that are currently being translated from the 'inside'.

stnNatGroupTotalFtpSessions.name: stnNatGroupTotalFtpSessions
stnNatGroupTotalFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that have been translated from the 'inside'.

stnNatGroupMissedFtpSessionLookups.name: stnNatGroupMissedFtpSessionLookups
stnNatGroupMissedFtpSessionLookups.description: The number of times an expired or unknown FTP client session was referenced.

stnNatGroupNoIdleFtpSessions.name: stnNatGroupNoIdleFtpSessions
stnNatGroupNoIdleFtpSessions.description: The number of times an FTP Client session was denied translation because there were no availible idle FTP sessions.

stnNatGroupNoIdleOutsideAddrs.name: stnNatGroupNoIdleOutsideAddrs
stnNatGroupNoIdleOutsideAddrs.description: The number of times a packet has arrived from a valid inside address, but a translation was not established because no outside address was availible. This value is ignored for static NAT.

stnNatGroupFoundIdleOutsideAddrs.name: stnNatGroupFoundIdleOutsideAddrs
stnNatGroupFoundIdleOutsideAddrs.description: The number of times a packet has arrived from a valid inside address and a translation was established due to the presence of an idle outside address. This value is ignored for static NAT.

stnNatGroupInsidePktMisses.name: stnNatGroupInsidePktMisses
stnNatGroupInsidePktMisses.description: The number of times a packet arrived from an inside address that did not have a translation programed. This value is ignored for static NAT.

stnNatGroupInsidePktHits.name: stnNatGroupInsidePktHits
stnNatGroupInsidePktHits.description: The number of times a packet arrived for an inside address that was among any the known inside addresses configured for the interface.

stnNatGroupOutsidePktMisses.name: stnNatGroupOutsidePktMisses
stnNatGroupOutsidePktMisses.description: The number of times a packet arrived for an outside address that did not have a translation programed. This value is ignored for static NAT.

stnNatGroupOutsidePktHits.name: stnNatGroupOutsidePktHits
stnNatGroupOutsidePktHits.description: The number of times a packet arrived for an outside address that was among any the known outside addresses configured for the interface.

stnNatGroupInvalidOutsidePktMisses.name: stnNatGroupInvalidOutsidePktMisses
stnNatGroupInvalidOutsidePktMisses.description: The number of times a packet arrived for an outside address that was not among any of the known outside addresses configured for the interface.

stnNatGroupInsideFlowOrigin.name: stnNatGroupInsideFlowOrigin
stnNatGroupInsideFlowOrigin.description: Indicates whether traffic entering (ingress) or leaving (egress) the router is considered to be originating from the 'inside' for this interface

stnNatGroupPortBaseNumber.name: stnNatGroupPortBaseNumber
stnNatGroupPortBaseNumber.description: This is the first port number in the range of port numbers that packets from the inside have their source port translated to. This value is valid only for NAT type PAT.

stnNatGroupPortEndNumber.name: stnNatGroupPortEndNumber
stnNatGroupPortEndNumber.description: This is the first port number in the range of port numbers that packets from the inside have their source port translated to. This value is valid only for NAT type PAT.

stnNatGroupMaxInsideAddrs.name: stnNatGroupMaxInsideAddrs
stnNatGroupMaxInsideAddrs.description: The number of inside addresses that can be translated from the 'inside' at one time. This value is valid only for NAT type PAT.

stnNatGroupMaxPortsPerInsideAddr.name: stnNatGroupMaxPortsPerInsideAddr
stnNatGroupMaxPortsPerInsideAddr.description: The number of port translations allowed any single 'inside' address at one time. This value is valid only for NAT type PAT.

stnNatGroupPortLimitReached.name: stnNatGroupPortLimitReached
stnNatGroupPortLimitReached.description: The number of times a packet has arrived from a valid inside address, but a translation was not established because the limit on the number of ports was reached. This value is valid only for NAT type PAT.

stnNatGroupInsideAddrLimitReached.name: stnNatGroupInsideAddrLimitReached
stnNatGroupInsideAddrLimitReached.description: The number of times a packet has arrived from a valid inside address, but a translation was not established because the limit on the number of inside addresses was reached. This value is valid only for NAT type PAT.

stnNatOutTransTable.name: stnNatOutTransTable
stnNatOutTransTable.description: A list of NAT translation entries indexed by outside address.

stnNatOutTransEntry.name: stnNatOutTransEntry
stnNatOutTransEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular NAT translation.

stnNatOutTransSubnetIfInstance.name: stnNatOutTransSubnetIfInstance
stnNatOutTransSubnetIfInstance.description: A sequence number that identifies a sub-network interface entry in the table.

stnNatOutTransOutsideBaseAddress.name: stnNatOutTransOutsideBaseAddress
stnNatOutTransOutsideBaseAddress.description: This is the first outside IP address in the range of outside addresses that packets from the inside have their source address translated to.

stnNatOutTransOutsideAddress.name: stnNatOutTransOutsideAddress
stnNatOutTransOutsideAddress.description: This is the outside IP address for the translation.

stnNatOutTransInsideAddress.name: stnNatOutTransInsideAddress
stnNatOutTransInsideAddress.description: This is the inside IP address for the translation.

stnNatOutTransMode.name: stnNatOutTransMode
stnNatOutTransMode.description: Indicates whether this translation is pooled, static or PAT

stnNatOutTransUpTimeSec.name: stnNatOutTransUpTimeSec
stnNatOutTransUpTimeSec.description: The number of seconds since this translation was started.

stnNatOutTransSecsSinceLastHit.name: stnNatOutTransSecsSinceLastHit
stnNatOutTransSecsSinceLastHit.description: The number of seconds since this translation was last used.

stnNatOutTransCurrentFtpSessions.name: stnNatOutTransCurrentFtpSessions
stnNatOutTransCurrentFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that are currently being translated from the 'inside' for this translation.

stnNatOutTransTotalFtpSessions.name: stnNatOutTransTotalFtpSessions
stnNatOutTransTotalFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that have been translated from the 'inside' for this translation.

stnNatOutTransInsidePktHits.name: stnNatOutTransInsidePktHits
stnNatOutTransInsidePktHits.description: The number of times a packet arrived for this inside address.

stnNatOutTransOutsidePktHits.name: stnNatOutTransOutsidePktHits
stnNatOutTransOutsidePktHits.description: The number of times a packet arrived for this outside address.

stnNatOutTransOutsidePortNumber.name: stnNatOutTransOutsidePortNumber
stnNatOutTransOutsidePortNumber.description: This is the outside port number for the translation.

stnNatOutTransInsidePortNumber.name: stnNatOutTransInsidePortNumber
stnNatOutTransInsidePortNumber.description: This is the inside port number for the translation.

stnNatOutTransOutsidePortsInuse.name: stnNatOutTransOutsidePortsInuse
stnNatOutTransOutsidePortsInuse.description: This is the number of ports currently being used by the outside address.

stnNatOutTransInsidePortsInuse.name: stnNatOutTransInsidePortsInuse
stnNatOutTransInsidePortsInuse.description: This is the number of ports currently being used by the inside address.

stnNatOutTransInsidePortLimitReached.name: stnNatOutTransInsidePortLimitReached
stnNatOutTransInsidePortLimitReached.description: This is the number of times the inside address reached its port limit.

stnNatInTransTable.name: stnNatInTransTable
stnNatInTransTable.description: A list of NAT translation entries indexed by inside address.

stnNatInTransEntry.name: stnNatInTransEntry
stnNatInTransEntry.description: Entry contains information about a particular NAT translation.

stnNatInTransSubnetIfInstance.name: stnNatInTransSubnetIfInstance
stnNatInTransSubnetIfInstance.description: A sequence number that identifies a sub-network interface entry in the table.

stnNatInTransOutsideBaseAddress.name: stnNatInTransOutsideBaseAddress
stnNatInTransOutsideBaseAddress.description: This is the first outside IP address in the range of outside addresses that packets from the inside have their source address translated to.

stnNatInTransOutsideAddress.name: stnNatInTransOutsideAddress
stnNatInTransOutsideAddress.description: This is the last outside IP address in the range of outside addresses that packets from the inside have their source address translated to.

stnNatInTransInsideAddress.name: stnNatInTransInsideAddress
stnNatInTransInsideAddress.description: This is inside IP address for the translation.

stnNatInTransMode.name: stnNatInTransMode
stnNatInTransMode.description: Indicates whether this translation is pooled, static or port based.

stnNatInTransUpTimeSec.name: stnNatInTransUpTimeSec
stnNatInTransUpTimeSec.description: The number of seconds since this translation was started.

stnNatInTransSecsSinceLastHit.name: stnNatInTransSecsSinceLastHit
stnNatInTransSecsSinceLastHit.description: The number of seconds since this translation was last used.

stnNatInTransCurrentFtpSessions.name: stnNatInTransCurrentFtpSessions
stnNatInTransCurrentFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that are currently being translated from the 'inside' for this translation.

stnNatInTransTotalFtpSessions.name: stnNatInTransTotalFtpSessions
stnNatInTransTotalFtpSessions.description: The number of FTP Client sessions that have been translated from the 'inside' for this translation.

stnNatInTransInsidePktHits.name: stnNatInTransInsidePktHits
stnNatInTransInsidePktHits.description: The number of times a packet arrived for this inside address.

stnNatInTransOutsidePktHits.name: stnNatInTransOutsidePktHits
stnNatInTransOutsidePktHits.description: The number of times a packet arrived for this outside address.

stnNatInTransOutsidePortNumber.name: stnNatInTransOutsidePortNumber
stnNatInTransOutsidePortNumber.description: This is the outside port number for the translation.

stnNatInTransInsidePortNumber.name: stnNatInTransInsidePortNumber
stnNatInTransInsidePortNumber.description: This is the inside port number for the translation.

stnNatInTransOutsidePortsInuse.name: stnNatInTransOutsidePortsInuse
stnNatInTransOutsidePortsInuse.description: This is the number of ports currently being used by the outside address.

stnNatInTransInsidePortsInuse.name: stnNatInTransInsidePortsInuse
stnNatInTransInsidePortsInuse.description: This is the number of ports currently being used by the inside address.

stnNatInTransInsidePortLimitReached.name: stnNatInTransInsidePortLimitReached
stnNatInTransInsidePortLimitReached.description: This is the number of times the inside address reached its port limit.
